{"tid":609932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"籃球機械人日本誕生 100%命中率嚇怕職業球員","createTime":"2018-03-29T12:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T13:14:34.000Z","uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"242dc54514ff9292b19b5ca99e5c79ab2f9f09ad","tid":609932,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T12:45:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180329/58007786\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180329%2F58007786&d=fxjA2VzlHrE%2B8MrzBOvQPjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=fdad9fcb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180329%2F58007786&h=610ac4b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180329/58007786</a><br />\n家陣不少電影都擔憂未來的世界可能被機械人操縱，其實唔係講笑。日本東京早前就有研發小組設計咗一個籃球機械人，結果呢位叫CUE嘅機械人，就喺周三一場職業籃球聯賽嘅半場期間正式亮相，同職業球員鬥射波，結果10射全中，準繩度高達100%，擊敗嗰位球員。<br />\n<br />\nCUE係由豐田技術協會中嘅17名志願者，為慶祝汽車製造商成立70周年而設計的，而佢哋其實唔算係正式電腦程式人員，但就用佢哋對汽車技術嘅知識嚟設計。未正式亮相前，協會已經發放過video證明6尺3寸嘅CUE射波有幾咁勁，據講CUE借助人工智能程式及超過20萬次試驗同練習，先可以去到百發百中境界。<br />\n<br />\n周三一場由Alvark Tokyo對Tochigi Brex嘅日本職業籃球聯賽，CUE就正式出現喺大家面前，半場時同職業球員鬥射波，結果10射全中，而球員就有兩球炒粉。睇嚟就算派史提芬居里上陣，同CUE鬥落去都一定會輸。"},{"pid":"eee46cde85e2ad927d3b3ed0983288bf2c288dcd","tid":609932,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T12:51:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fJeeF773Fmc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfJeeF773Fmc&d=fxjA2VzlHrE%2B8MrzBOvQPjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=fa68bcff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fJeeF773Fmc</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fdd5631bb31cca1902cfb4d713cf1096e3a6ee3","tid":609932,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T12:58:18.000Z","msg":"睇片好似係同一個位射<br />\n咁同櫻木花道淨係識在罰球線45度射差唔多"},{"pid":"7abe0e5e099e86e7c4ff92764d4180f3547c6b57","tid":609932,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:04:19.000Z","msg":"計曬角度點射都得啦"},{"pid":"d2894fa87abb8d568175cb87e80f1000e644ed3e","tid":609932,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:10:07.000Z","msg":"夠膽就黎一場1on1"},{"pid":"da27aa7415e64235e81418acbda70d5695cd4fd8","tid":609932,"uid":102096,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:12:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de2b63a5352b5e04e7fd9e22ba843131d9f8b3f0","tid":609932,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:14:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以話籃波真係一種好on9運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以話____真係一種好on9運動"}]}